[30;1m186 | [0m[35m   ``device.read_configuration()`` and captures that information the first time[0m

[30;1m555 | [0m[35m  ``__init__subclass__``.  There are now no meta-classes used in ophyd![0m
[30;1m556 | [0m[35m* Completely overhauled how we connect to PVs at initialization and tear them[0m
[30;1m557 | [0m[35m  down on destruction of the ophyd objects.[0m
[30;1m558 | [0m[35m* Completely overhauled how PV meta-data is handled.[0m
[30;1m559 | [0m[35m* Completely overhauled the dispatcher thread mechanism.[0m

[30;1m120 | [0m[35mcompletion will be called immediately, and no reference will be held.[0m
